The kingdom which earli=
er appeared to him to be a burden did not trouble him
later when he became =
a Jnani. All that I want to say is, how do others know
about the happiness =
of bhiksha? There is nothing great about begging or
eating food from a leaf=
 which is thrown out after taking food from it.

